text.tspan: we take active ownership of our careers! Choose your own direction and decide what actions will best solve the
challenges you will face. Each round represents a year; record your career progression over the years and com
pare your journey to that of your colleagues’.
All players will be dealt 5 Action Cards to start and will draw an additional
card at the beginning of each round.
Roll 2 dice to decide how many spaces you will move each round. If
doubles, roll the dice a second time.
When passing a Challenge Point, stop and draw a Challenge Card. Play
any Action Card to continue moving your remaining spaces past the
Challenge Point. End your turn if you have no Action Cards to play.
Draw 3 Action Cards when visiting a hub (Management Mountain, etc.).
You must pass a challenge point before revisiting a hub to draw additional
At the end of each round, record any challenges, actions, and any hubs
that you have visited for the year.
